vistra.framework.util.palette

Enum StrokePalette

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<StrokePalette>
      • vistra.framework.util.palette.StrokePalette
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<StrokePalette>

    public enum StrokePalette
extends java.lang.Enum<StrokePalette>
    A palette defining some customized strokes.

    Use the lower-case constants for getting directly a BasicStroke.

    Author:
    Roland Bruggmann (brugr9@bfh.ch)
    See Also:
    FontPalette, ColorPalette, ShapePalette
